{
  "content": [
    {"type": "sound", "sound_type": "bgm", "file_path": "BgmTest0"},
    {"type": "talk", "is_center": "1", "talk_content": "[font_size=22]深夜便利店[/font_size]\n\n[color=#888]—— 一个短篇测试剧本 ——[/color]"},
    {"type": "background", "file_path": "BgTest0", "wait_tween_end": "1"},
    {"type": "talk", "talker": "店长", "talk_content": "欢迎光临。这么晚了，要点什么？"},
    {"type": "tachie", "tachies": {"shopkeeper": {"file_path": "TachiTest0", "slot": "Center"}}},
    {"type": "talk", "talker": "我", "talk_content": "随便看看。"},
    {"type": "talk", "is_center": "1", "talk_content": "（我扫了一眼货架。三明治、泡面、能量饮料。和千千万万的便利店没有区别。）"},
    {"type": "talk", "is_center": "1", "talk_content": "（但他不一样。他的眼睛在收银台后面打量着我，像在掂量什么。）"},
    {"type": "talk", "talker": "店长", "talk_content": "你是外地来的吧。"},
    {"type": "tachie", "tachies": {"shopkeeper": {"file_path": "TachiTest0", "type": "change"}}},
    {"type": "talk", "talker": "店长", "talk_content": "我在这守了二十年了。见过很多像你这样的人。"},
    {"type": "talk", "talker": "我", "talk_content": "什么意思？"},
    {"type": "talk", "talker": "店长", "talk_content": "你后半夜两点进的城。没有行李。没有预订酒店。你在找什么东西。"},
    {"type": "talk", "is_center": "1", "talk_content": "（他说对了。但我不能说。）"},
    {"type": "talk", "talker": "我", "talk_content": "我只是路过。"},
    {"type": "tachie", "tachies": {"shopkeeper": {"file_path": "TachiTest0", "type": "onlyShow"}}},
    {"type": "talk", "talker": "店长", "talk_content": "你[rainbow]撒谎[/rainbow]的水平很差。但没关系——今晚我也不想惹麻烦。"},
    {"type": "talk", "talker": "店长", "talk_content": "听好了。沿着这条路往前走，第三个路口右转，你会看到一座废弃的水塔。你想要的答案在那里。"},
    {"type": "talk", "is_center": "1", "talk_content": "（我愣住了。他怎么知道我找什么？）"},
    {"type": "talk", "talker": "我", "talk_content": "你是谁？"},
    {"type": "tachie", "tachies": {"shopkeeper": {"type": "close"}}},
    {"type": "talk", "is_center": "1", "talk_content": "（收银台后面没有人了。）"},
    {"type": "talk", "is_center": "1", "talk_content": "（便利店里只有荧光灯的嗡嗡声。门外的风铃轻轻响了一下。）"},
    {"type": "event", "event_name": "shopkeeper_vanished"},
    {"type": "talk", "is_center": "1", "talk_content": "（我在空无一人的柜台前站了很久。）"},
    {"type": "branch", "options": {
      "go_tower": {"text": "前往废弃水塔"},
      "call_police": {"text": "拨打报警电话"},
      "go_home": {"text": "转身离开，忘掉这一切", "wait": "2.0"}
    }},
    {"type": "talk", "talker": "我", "talk_content": "管不了那么多了。我得去看看。", "branch": "go_tower"},
    {"type": "background", "file_path": "BgTest1", "wait_tween_end": "1", "branch": "go_tower"},
    {"type": "talk", "is_center": "1", "talk_content": "水塔矗立在月光下。铁梯上生满红锈，发出嘎吱嘎吱的声音。", "branch": "go_tower"},
    {"type": "talk", "is_center": "1", "talk_content": "塔顶有一个铁盒。里面放着一张泛黄的照片和一个地址。", "branch": "go_tower"},
    {"type": "talk", "is_center": "1", "talk_content": "—— To Be Continued ——", "branch": "go_tower", "wait": "3"},
    {"type": "talk", "is_center": "1", "talk_content": "（我掏出手机，拨下了号码。但听筒里只有沙沙的电流声。）", "branch": "call_police"},
    {"type": "talk", "is_center": "1", "talk_content": "（一个声音从电流声中缓缓浮现，听起来很像那个店长。）", "branch": "call_police"},
    {"type": "talk", "talker": "电话那头", "talk_content": "你比我想的聪明。但不该找他们。来找我。", "branch": "call_police"},
    {"type": "talk", "is_center": "1", "talk_content": "—— To Be Continued ——", "branch": "call_police", "wait": "3"},
    {"type": "talk", "is_center": "1", "talk_content": "（我推开门，走进夜色。什么都没有发生。）", "branch": "go_home"},
    {"type": "talk", "is_center": "1", "talk_content": "（但到家后，我发现门口的鞋柜上放着一罐我没买过的咖啡。）", "branch": "go_home"},
    {"type": "talk", "is_center": "1", "talk_content": "（便利店的收据。上面的时间是——三分钟之后。）", "branch": "go_home"},
    {"type": "talk", "is_center": "1", "talk_content": "—— Bad End ——", "branch": "go_home", "wait": "3"}
  ]
}
